history.content: Unfortunately, although we try to avoid them, conflicts happen every semester due to many scheduling constraints. The faculty have not communicated that they do not want these two classes to conflict. If you feel that these are common classes to take together, I invite you to contact the faculty and share your concern. As enrollment has already begun, these classes will not be moved at this time.

I am trying to schedule my classes for next semester and I want to take EE 120 and EE 130, but all times conflict. That is, there is no way to take 120 and 130 together next semester. Can this please be fixed? I know this will help a lot of other people since 120 and 130 are popular upper divisions to take in EE right after 16A and 16B.

Thanks!
history.subject: EE 120 and EE 130 Conflicts
